#
# besticon is the chosen Axis 41 Go-side continuation
# because:
#   - It uses PuerkitoBio/goquery v1.12 as a DIRECT
#     dependency in go.mod (modern v1.12 not the
#     ancient v1.5 some candidates pinned to)
#   - It has a clean, focused CLI binary (`besticon
#     <URL>`) — not just a framework or library
#   - The favicon-extraction use case is a textbook
#     HTML-scraping pipeline: fetch HTML, parse
#     <head>, query <link> + <meta> tags via CSS
