#     URLs, fetch the icon assets
#   - It is the closest functional analog to email-
#     sleuth (R753) — both do "fetch HTML page,
#     extract attribute-based data from specific
#     elements" using their language's canonical
#     HTML-parsing library
#   - 988 stars + active maintenance since 2015
#     (decade+ continuity) make it a stable choice
#     for the taxonomy
#   - Author Matthias Lüdtke's standing in the
#     German Go community (XING + ex-Phrase/
#     Crealytics) adds provenance
