# Pending companion pick for Axis 41:
#   - TS-Node=96: a Node.js CLI tool prominently
#            using cheeriojs/cheerio (the dominant
#            Node HTML parsing + CSS-selector library;
#            ~29k stars; jQuery-inspired API for
#            Node) for HTML scraping
